## Installation
<div class="termy">

```console
pip install LucidDynamodb
```

</div>

**Note:**  <a href="https://gist.github.com/dineshsonachalam/88f55b28c1f0c1ce93421f5a8f33e84a"> Prerequisite for Python3 development </a>

